Exercises: If teacher-branded exercises are required and the library lacks them, the prewrite step creates them from the teacher\'92s knowledge base (patterns, prompts) with the same provenance note; exercise validator checks presence/structure, otherwise the prebuild fails.\
Assembly: Lookup-only\'97if required teacher stories/exercises aren\'92t present, assemble fails; no runtime authoring or auto-rewrite.\
