\
## Platform Adaptation Layer (PAL)\
\
Important distinction:\
\
**PAL does NOT belong inside V4 assembly.**\
\
Instead:\
\
1. V4 outputs a **canonical text artifact**\
2. PAL consumes that artifact and:\
\
   * fragments it\
   * clips it\
   * adapts it for TikTok / YouTube / Podcast\
\
This preserves:\
\
* determinism\
* book identity\
* auditability\
\
So PAL stays **downstream**, unchanged.\
\
---\
\
## Modules (90-day plan, etc.)\
\
These map cleanly to:\
\
* **Optional appended chapters**\
* or **format-specific chapter blocks**\
\
No runtime injection needed.\
\
